caption.p: Inhibitory effects on MDA-MB-231 and SW620 cell proliferation with increasing concentrations (0–100 mg/mL) for 48 h of ( A) T. articulata trunk bark complete essential oil (HEE); ( B) Fraction E.1; ( C) Fraction E.2; ( D) Fraction E.3; ( E) Fraction E.4; ( F) Fraction E.5; ( G) 5-fluorouracil. The percentage of cell viability was determined using crystal violet assay. Results are expressed as mean percentage of control growth ± SD of three independent experiments.
